{"about_the_game":"<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">\ud83d\udc98<strong>Love n Life: Happy Student</strong>\ud83d\udc98</h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3149980/extras/keyartA_Storepage.jpg?t=1739443501\" /></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">At Reborn Entertainment, creativity drives everything we do as we\u2019re committed to delivering fresh experiences. For us, fun isn\u2019t just a goal\u2014it\u2019s the rule. Incorporating the Inventory Management system in Love n Life: Happy Student brings the excitement of dating to life in a way you\u2019ve never seen before. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">\u2b50\u00a0<strong>Story</strong> </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">You're a third-year college student living in the suburbs. After taking a competitive exam, you\u2019re lucky enough to transfer to the prestigious Lingyun University, an elite school reserved for the best of the best. Upon arrival, you\u2019re placed in an old dorm, where your exciting new student life begins.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3149980/extras/D2_Girl_C_keyart_3.jpg?t=1739443501\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3149980/extras/keyartB_Storepage.png?t=1739443501\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">\u2b50\u00a0<strong>Gameplay</strong> </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">In Love n Life: Happy Student, you'll interact with various ladies, each with her own personality and preferences. The innovative inventory management system adds a fresh twist to the dating sim genre, where the items you collect and manage can influence your relationships and interactions. Balance your time, resources, and decisions to create meaningful connections and explore multiple story paths. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">\u2b50\u00a0<strong>Features</strong> </h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Experience dating through the unique Inventory Management system!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Give presentations, read books, play basketball, and engage in charity work in Daily Activities.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Try your hand at fishing and cooking in mini-games.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Complete Girls\u2019 Missions and Side Missions.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Beautiful girls come to life with Live2D animations.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Choose your words carefully\u2014your choices affect affection levels with Dynamic Conversations.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Stay connected with social apps, texting, collections, and more using your phone.</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">\u2b50<strong>The ladies:</strong></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">\ud83d\udc98\u00a0<strong>Liu Yating</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3149980/extras/ezgif-6-4a24f9e136.gif?t=1739443501\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">You're in the same class as a beautiful, carefree girl who loves to explore new things. She\u2019s destined to become your best friend.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">\ud83d\udc98\u00a0<strong>Chen Meiling</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3149980/extras/ezgif-6-cb7f25df84.gif?t=1739443501\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The literature teacher at your school and the dorm manager where you live. With her sweet, kind, and playful personality, she\u2019s the teacher every student loves having in class!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">\ud83d\udc98\u00a0<strong>Qin Yilin</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3149980/extras/ezgif-1-2515c056b1.gif?t=1739443501\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">&quot;Only knowledge and discipline create elite students. Without them, you're dust.&quot; The Student Council President is cool, elegant, and well-organized. She\u2019s determined to push every student to reach their highest potential\u2014no matter what it takes!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">\ud83d\udc98\u00a0<strong>Luna-3X</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3149980/extras/ezgif-1-37d320905a.gif?t=1739443501\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">She is your funny, lively, and lovely virtual assistant who often acts silly and makes you laugh. Luna-3X is hardworking, obedient, and never gets jealous, even when you are dating other ladies.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3149980/extras/wl_eng.gif?t=1739443501\" /></p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3149980/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1739443501","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3149980/page.bg.jpg?t=1739443501","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3149980/cccd3bc1b8a8aec2e297c6496615b1162f775057/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1739443501","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3149980/cccd3bc1b8a8aec2e297c6496615b1162f775057/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1739443501","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Steam Achievements","id":22},{"description":"Steam Cloud","id":23},{"description":"Remote Play Together","id":44}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"detailed_description":"<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">\ud83d\udc98<strong>Love n Life: Happy Student</strong>\ud83d\udc98</h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/stor